race.description: RMBL Investments Rising Stars Race Handicap (Bm56)
race.comment: Looks a very winnable race for SHE'S IMPECCABLE (8) post scratchings. She comes through a race at Terang when working home well without threat for a narrow fifth having been close up prior. She's going well without winning and this apprentice only race could see a few go quicker up front. IL CIELO (7) has been good in two runs back, fourth in a stronger race at Pakenham last time. He has a 4kg claimer on which will be interesting but on form he's a strong winning chance. ALGADON STORM (9) is going well, solid without the best of runs at Cranbourne last time out. She draws nicely here for Rose Hammond who can have last crack. KHANT BEE (12) resumes. He'll get further but has one of the better jockeys in the race in Ryan Houston aboard and will be finishing strongly.
